LU-18857 mgs: add timeout mechanism for allow_register

Add automatic timeout functionality to the allow_register
parameter to improve security by limiting the window
during which new filesystems or targets can register.

Support three modes:
 allow_register=0: Registration disabled
 allow_register=1: Registration enabled with 1 hour timeout
 allow_register=N: Registration enabled with N seconds timeout

Timer automatically disables registration when timeout expires

Add test_163b to verify the functionality

